commit.message: fix bugs in comparison of mock.call objects with tricky parameter objects.
Add support for non-deterministic logging order.

Fix compare() of Mock.call_args[_list] against call() objects

mock.call() objects may be 2-tuples or 3-tuples

Fixes #130
include optional deps needed for docs
have doc builds blow up on warnings
Make API docs a little easier to navigate.

Allow the attributes to be ignored to be specified at call time, rather than just in the context.

This is handy for writing comparers for types where a specified attribute or two need to be ignored.
make check_raises usable in function-based tests.
Fix bug when comparing strings with slotted objects that have the same repr.
add support for universal_newlines, text, encoding and errors to MockPopen
